rich-text.text: Man, I wanna send my girlfriend to Shanghai, China. She is now at home
I wanna her safe and cound arrive there tomorrow 12 p.m.
Moreover, since she never comes to China, please find a driver to take her to my home.
Yes, sir. Could you please provide a photo of her so that our delivery man could recogonize her?
OMG! What a lovely girl! Sir, here is our deliver plan, please check.

The deliverman will arrange an airline to help the user's girlfried go to Shanghai. Because she does not know about Shanghai, the deliverman will protect her, help find a car and drive her to the destination.
